ative;\">  가. 본교 학부생 3학년 이상 (2026-1학기 졸업 또는 수료예정자 지원 불가)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  나. 어학성적 우수자 우대 (IELTS 6.0 / TOEFL IBT 72 중 1개 이상)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">3. 신청기간: 2026 . 4. 1(수) ~ 4. 7(화) 13시까지</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">4. 신청방법 : nDRIMS 신청([학생신청]신청함 &gt; 국제교류)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  ※ 국제교류신청 '2026/여름학기' 및 언어권 '영어' 선택</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">※ 수학계획서는 영문으로 4,000자 이내로 작성 - 수학계획서 상단에 희망하는 프로그램 (Sustainable Business / Cross Cultural Management) 중 택 1하여 작성</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">5. 선발방법</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> 가. 신청인원이 모집인원을 초과하지 않을 경우, 서류평가만으로 선발</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> 나. 신청인원이 모집인원을 초과할 경우, 면접 진행 예정</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'> </p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">6. 유의사항</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> 가. 프로그램비가 포함하는 사항을 확인하고, 그 외 발생하는</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">행정수수료, 항공권, 숙박비, 교통비 등은 학생 부담</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> 나. 현지 사정 및 자매대학교 사정으로 인해 프로그램이 취소될 수 있음</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> 다. 동국대학교에서 선발하더라도 자매대학에서 선발하지 않을 수 있으며, 자매대학 입학허가서를 </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">받아야 최종선발이 확정됨</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> 라. 2026 하계 해외 단기 연수 프로그램 중복지원 불가 (영어권 및 타 언어권 프로그램 합격(합격을 포기한 경우에도) 후 중복지원 불가)</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'> </p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'> </p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"font-family: tahoma; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">7. 문의: 02-2260-3464 / outbound1@dongguk.edu.  끝.</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'> </p>",
